<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.7">
<l>paṭaṅkaḷ palavu muṭaippām paraiyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">paṭarpū miyaittāṅ kikiṭap pavaṉpōl</l>
<l>taṭaṅkai viralain tumalara vaittut</l>
<l rend="indent">tāmō taraṉtāṅ kutaṭa varaitāṉ</l>
<l>aṭaṅkac ceṉṟilaṅ kaiyaiyī ṭaḻitta</l>
<l rend="indent">vaṉumaṉ pukaḻpā ṭitaṅkuṭ ṭaṉkaḷai</l>
<l>kuṭaṅkaik koṇṭuman tikaḷkaṇ vaḷarttuṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The huge mountain that Dāmodara bore</l>
<l>[by] spreading the five fingers of [his] broad hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">Like the king of the serpents, [his] many hoods spread,</l>
<l rend="indent">who bore the vast earth in repose,</l>
<l>Called Govardhana,</l>
<l rend="indent">Where female monkeys, taking their young</l>
<l rend="indent">in the palm of [their] hands, put [them] to sleep,</l>
<l rend="indent">Singing the glory of Hanuman who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having gone to Laṅkā, utterly annihilated [its] might,</l>
<l>Is [his] victory umbrella.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
